          <h2>Summer Medals won per participation</h2>
          <p>The map above shows the average number of medals won by each country each time they perticipate in the Summer Olympics. The United States of America are far ahead
            of any other country, while China, Russia, Germany and the United Kingdom remain competitive. Majority of the countries that perform well in the Olympics 
            are also global superpowers while some developing countries have also managed to win medals in the Summer sports.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
