            <h2>Summer Performance vs. Population</h2>
            <p>The graph on the right shows the number of medals won in the Summer Olympics plotted against the population of the country. The general trend shows that 
                countries with larger populations tend to perform better at the Summer Olympics. Additionally, the most successful continent in general is Europe.
            </p>
